<p begin="00:00:12.012" end="00:00:18.252" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">TONIGHT A JOURNALIST WHO HAS </span><span style="block">WRITTEN "BITTER PILL" WHY </span><span style="block">MEDICAL BILLS ARE KILLING US.</span></p>


<p begin="00:00:18.252" end="00:00:25.359" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">PLEASE WELCOME TO THE PROGRAM </span><span style="block">STEPHEN BRILL.</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:25.359" end="00:00:26.660" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">[CHEERS AND APPLAUSE]</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:26.660" end="00:00:28.462" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THIS IS -- THANKS FOR COMING ON.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:28.462" end="00:00:30.631" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THIS IS AN UNBELIEVABLE ARTICLE.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:30.631" end="00:00:33.567" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IT'S CALLED WHY MEDICAL BILLS </span><span style="block">ARE KILLING US.</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:33.567" end="00:00:37.671" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I'M ACCUSTOMED TO BEING ANGRY --</span></p>
