<p begin="00:00:42.309" end="00:00:50.417" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">-- READ "TIME" MAGAZINE COVER </span><span style="block">STORIES MOSTLY BECAUSE IT'S </span><span style="block">LIKE" ARE ANGELS REAL"?</span></p>


<p begin="00:00:50.417" end="00:01:03.764" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BUT THIS IS 36 PAGES OF </span><span style="block">INCREDIBLY THOROUG JOURNAL -- I </span><span style="block">FORGOT HOW TO PRONOUNCE IT.</span></p>


<p begin="00:01:03.764" end="00:01:05.065" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; COULD YOU CALL IT REPORTING.</span></p>
