<p begin="00:02:09.796" end="00:02:15.502" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; WHY SHOULD THERE BE?</span></p>
<p begin="00:02:15.502" end="00:02:21.775" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IF YOU BUY SHOES, A RICH GUY </span><span style="block">LIKE YOU BUYING A $200 PAIR --</span></p>

<p begin="00:02:21.775" end="00:02:22.609" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: SURE.</span></p>
<p begin="00:02:22.609" end="00:02:25.946" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">LET ME SAY THIS TIMBERLAND'S </span><span style="block">DON'T COME CHEAP.</span></p>

<p begin="00:02:25.946" end="00:02:28.949" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; NO, I KNOW.</span></p>
<p begin="00:02:28.949" end="00:02:32.219" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU GO TO A STORE AND WANT TO </span><span style="block">BUY SHOES.</span></p>

<p begin="00:02:32.219" end="00:02:33.086" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: THAT'S RIGHT.</span></p>
<p begin="00:02:33.086" end="00:02:39.126" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; INSTEAD OF $200 THE GUY SAYS </span><span style="block">THAT IS $6,000.</span></p>

<p begin="00:02:39.126" end="00:02:41.662" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU CAN DECIDE NOT TO BUY THE </span><span style="block">SHOES.</span></p>

<p begin="00:02:41.662" end="00:02:46.567" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BETTER YET YOU CAN GO UP THE </span><span style="block">BLOCK AND SEE IF THEY HAVE A </span><span style="block">DIFFERENT PRICE.</span></p>


<p begin="00:02:46.567" end="00:02:48.502" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">NONE OF THAT HAPPENS WITH HEALTH </span><span style="block">CARE.</span></p>

<p begin="00:02:48.502" end="00:02:52.739" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU ARE AN INVOLUNTARY ENTERING </span><span style="block">TO THE MARKETPLACE.</span></p>

