<p begin="00:03:45.626" end="00:03:49.963" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; THE PEOPLE WHO RUN LABS AND </span><span style="block">TESTS AND GOD KNOWS THE PEOPLE </span><span style="block">WHO RUN THE HOSPITAL THEY ARE</span></p>


