<p begin="00:03:57.237" end="00:03:59.706" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THERE ARE TWO ECONOMIES IN THIS </span><span style="block">COUNTRY.</span></p>

<p begin="00:03:59.706" end="00:04:03.610" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THERE'S THE ECONOMIES OF ALL OF </span><span style="block">US AND THE ISLAND, HEALTH CARE </span><span style="block">ECONOMY.</span></p>


<p begin="00:04:03.610" end="00:04:08.348" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">WE'VE HAD A PRETTY ROUGH TIME </span><span style="block">OVER THE LAST FOUR OR FIVES, SIX </span><span style="block">YEARS IN OUR ECONOMY.</span></p>


<p begin="00:04:08.348" end="00:04:11.852" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THERE'S A LOT OF UNEMPLOYMENT, A </span><span style="block">LOT OF PRESSURE ON US.</span></p>

<p begin="00:04:11.852" end="00:04:14.054" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">NOT ON THAT ISLAND.</span></p>
<p begin="00:04:14.054" end="00:04:16.123" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">EVERYBODY JUST KEEPS MAKING MORE </span><span style="block">MONEY.</span></p>

