<p begin="00:04:26.867" end="00:04:31.338" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">60% OF THE PERSONAL BANKRUPTCIES </span><span style="block">IN THIS COUNTRY COME FROM </span><span style="block">MEDICAL BILLS.</span></p>


<p begin="00:04:31.338" end="00:04:35.175" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: WHAT IS CRAZY TO ME IS </span><span style="block">WHEN YOU BEGIN TO TEASE IT </span><span style="block">APART.</span></p>


