<p begin="00:04:40.380" end="00:04:42.416" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">AS I'M READING IT'S 36 PAGES.</span></p>
<p begin="00:04:42.416" end="00:04:52.226" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">AS YOU GET HIGHER AND HIGHER IN </span><span style="block">THE PAGES YOU FEEL LIKE CHUCK </span><span style="block">YAEGER BREAKING THE SOUND </span><span style="block">BARRIER.</span></p>



<p begin="00:04:52.226" end="00:04:53.861" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I WAS LIKE OH, MY GOD.</span></p>
<p begin="00:04:53.861" end="00:04:56.930" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BY PAGE TEN I WAS LIKE I CAN'T </span><span style="block">TAKE IT ANYMORE.</span></p>

<p begin="00:04:56.930" end="00:04:58.832" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THERE'S SOMETHING -- YOU CANNOT </span><span style="block">BELIEVE THIS.</span></p>

