<p begin="00:05:03.637" end="00:05:08.509" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">SO IF YOU WANT AN MRI THAT'S </span><span style="block">$6,000 ACCORDING TO THE CHARGE </span><span style="block">MASTER.</span></p>


<p begin="00:05:08.509" end="00:05:10.911" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IF YOU GOOD THROUGH MEDICARE </span><span style="block">IT'S $500.</span></p>

