<p begin="00:05:43.277" end="00:05:47.915" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU PAY FOR A SURGEONS GOWN IN </span><span style="block">THE OPERATING ROOM IN ADDITION </span><span style="block">TO PAYING FOR THE ROOM.</span></p>


